items.title: Astros slug past M's, claim first AL West crown
items.summary: A chance to clinch the American League West title and the home debut of Justin Verlander had the Astros in the mood to party on Sunday afternoon at Minute Maid Park.
items.content: A chance to clinch the American League West title and the home debut of Justin Verlander had the Astros in the mood to party on Sunday afternoon at Minute Maid Park.

items.title: Vintage Verlander K's 10 as Astros clinch West
items.summary: The Astros brought in Justin Verlander to pitch in big situations, and the veteran right-hander delivered on Sunday afternoon.
